c: 25
v: 19
t: "(God will say:) \"So they have denied you (who falsely worship them) in all that you assert regarding them, and you can neither ward off (your due punishment) nor obtain any help (from those you falsely deified and worshipped while in the world).\" (O people!) Whoever commits the greatest wrong (by associating partners with God), We will cause him to taste a great punishment"